Multi-questing does not mean to do the same quest over and over. It means that 2 people can do the same quest with 2 different components that the NPC wants. First one turns in their item, When the npc asks for the other item the second one turns theirs in. Both people have to have the item in the trade window with the npc. The last person that turns in their item recieves the reward.

